title: A Killer On The Run
description:
5 X 15 mins

Kenneth Noye is a career criminal, who is now safely under lock and key. He was involved with the heft of gold bullion in the "Brinks Mat" robbery and was found not guilty in dubious circumstances of the murder of an undercover policeman. When he became the chief suspect in the case of the murder of another motorist in a road rage incident, he became one of Britain's mos wanted criminals.
